      "data": {
        "title": "Start A Tiny Graph",
        "body": "Now ask for a tiny graph on a simple topic. The safest first request is: declaration for identity, one reader port exposed by the declaration, one markdown node for content, and optional portal behavior only if something needs to target an exposed surface. Then iterate from there.",
        "tag": "Concept",
