    {
      "id": "bootstrap-llm-handshake-sample",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Handshake Prompt",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -1216.7860170069953,
        "y": -422.71023115858435
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 320,
      "handles": [
        {
          "id": "root",
          "label": "root",
          "direction": "bidirectional",
          "dataType": "value",
          "angle": 210
        },
        {
          "id": "top",
          "label": "top",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "angle": 270
        },
        {
          "id": "right",
          "label": "right",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "angle": 360
        }
      ],
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "root",
          "label": "root",
          "direction": "bidirectional",
          "dataType": "value",
          "angle": 210
        },
        {
          "id": "top",
          "label": "top",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "angle": 270
        },
        {
          "id": "right",
          "label": "right",
          "direction": "output",
          "dataType": "any",
          "angle": 360
        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "root",
          "label": "root",
          "type": "value"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "key": "root",
          "label": "root",
          "type": "value"
        },
        {
          "key": "top",
          "label": "top",
          "type": "any"
        },
        {
          "key": "right",
          "label": "right",
          "type": "any"
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-bootstrap-llm"
        },
        "markdown": "# Twilite Bootstrap Handshake\n---\n\n## You can copy this node into your chatbot directly to get started.\n\nThis handshake is the same contract taught in:\n\n- `https://twilite.zone/library/documentation/contracts/onboarding.md`\n\nUse that onboarding guide as the canonical source.\n\n### What The Handshake Proves\nThe handshake proves that an agent can:\n- read the declaration-first model\n- distinguish declaration, markdown, port, and portal\n- create valid nodes with the current JSON shape\n- continue working without reintroducing old title/type/view scaffolding\n\n### Primitive Survival Model\nBefore asking for larger mutations, the model should understand:\n- `declaration` gives the graph identity and exposure contract\n- `markdown` is the safest default content primitive\n- `port` exposes a surface or semantic entry point\n- `portal` targets an exposed thing and chooses behavior\n\n### Required Response Shape\n- return JSON only\n- return one additive `transaction`\n- use one `createNodes` command\n- create one or two simple nodes only\n- use `action`, not `actions`\n- use `action`, not `command`\n- use `id`, not `uuid`\n- use `data`, not `metadata`\n- use explicit `position`, `width`, and `height`\n- include `visible: true` and `showLabel: true`\n- use `root` as the safe default port when unsure\n- use `reference` as the safe default edge type\n\n### Bootstrap Context\n- a new graph may start blank\n- declaration becomes required when the graph is becoming a real saved artifact\n- graph title belongs in `declaration.identity.name`\n- graph kind belongs in `declaration.intent.kind`\n- `port` exposes and `portal` acts on that exposure\n- `bridge` and `script` are advanced primitives, not the normal starting point\n- if declaration already exists, persistent local nodes should carry `data.identity.graphId`\n- if declaration does not exist yet, exploratory handshake nodes may be provisional\n\n### Placement Guidance\nFor a simple handshake:\n- place the declaration at the left or upper-left\n- place the handshake markdown nearby\n- keep the graph small and readable\n\nSafe starter sizes:\n- declaration: `360 x 220`\n- markdown: `260 x 220`\n\n### Example\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"transaction\",\n  \"commands\": [\n    {\n      \"action\": \"createNodes\",\n      \"nodes\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"handshake-note\",\n          \"type\": \"markdown\",\n          \"label\": \"Handshake\",\n          \"position\": { \"x\": 140, \"y\": -40 },\n          \"width\": 260,\n          \"height\": 220,\n          \"visible\": true,\n          \"showLabel\": true,\n          \"data\": {\n            \"markdown\": \"# Handshake received\\n\\nI am ready to make small valid Twilite graph mutations.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```",
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
          "state": "manually-shaped",
          "source": "manual",
          "updatedAt": 1781132787844,
          "reason": "node-drag"
        }
      }
    },
